data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select top(1) T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRD_ID, T1.CLT_IDENTIFIER from CKT_CASH_RECEIPT T2 join CKT_CR_DETAIL T1 on (T1.CRD_ID = @crdId) and (T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CST_IDENTIFIER = T1.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CASH_RECEIPT_ID = @cashReceiptId)

data.name: ReadCollectionType
data.value: select top(1) COLLECTION_TYPE_ID, PRINT_NAME, CODE, NAME, CASH_NON_CASH_IND, DISBURSEMENT_IND, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, DESCRIPTION from CKT_COLLTN_TYPE where COLLECTION_TYPE_ID = @collectionTypeId
